==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: ornamental
<hw>or`na*men"tal</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>ornemental</ets>.]</ety> <def>Serving to ornament; characterized by
ornament; beautifying; embellishing.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Some think it most <qex>ornamental</qex> to wear their bracelets
on their wrists; others, about their ankles.</q> <rj><qau>Sir T.
Browne.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>ornamentally</ent>⟦br⟧
